     Alphabet Robots Mahjong 2 is a fun and energizing way to play
     mahjong solitaire while learning English letter and number
     recognition and pronunciation at the same time! All of the letters
     and numbers are designed with an eye-popping robot monster theme
     and then placed onto brushed metal tiles. The metal tiles are
     placed into floating structures which you can rotate around to find
     the matching tiles. This is a game that the entire family can enjoy
     for hours of fun as you eliminate all of the tiles from the
     structures.

     It comes with 28 puzzle layouts and all puzzles are laid out using
     random letters and random tile orders so you can play the same
     puzzle again and again with it never being the same. Letter or
     number pronunciation occurs when a match is made. We think this is
     a great game for young students or adults learning English as a
     second language and have also seen it being enjoyed by children of
     all ages regardless of their primary language!
     Within each of the 4 robot laboratories there are 7 puzzles. The
     first 2 puzzles are all uppercase, the second 2 all lowercase and
     in the final 3 you can match uppercase and lowercase letters to
     each other. Every now and then a few number tiles are thrown in
     just to keep it extra interesting.

     Features:

     - An eye-popping robot monster theme that will keep the whole family
       inspired!
     - 28 different puzzle layouts with a different puzzle each time.
     - All tiles are always open. If you can click it you can select it.
     - A powerful point and star system designed to help keep you focused.
     - Letter and number pronunciation occurs in English when a match is
       made.
     - Invigorating background music throughout the game.
